out of that door alive.

01:39:32.117 --> 01:39:35.817
I am really, really excited

01:39:35.850 --> 01:39:38.783
to meet the rest
of your family.

01:39:40.917 --> 01:39:42.117
Especially Claire.

01:39:42.151 --> 01:39:44.884
I swear to God,
if you touch her...

01:39:44.917 --> 01:39:46.783
